customised tags

attributes = unique element
	eg
	<book price = "55" currency = "USD">  </book>
	
Name Spaces
	xmlns = xml name space
	elements would be set to the default namespace unless specified
	
	***Defined all at the same time
	
	eg
	<xmlns:a = urla>
		NOT DEFAULT NAMESPACE	
	<a:anything> </a:anything>

	name space can be overwritten with other predefined parent ones
	name space would not be overwritten by siblings' namespaces prefix
	
	
