JSON

	very lightweight
	derived from JavaScript
	simple definitions for keys and values(complex bit)
	[] means list (order is important/ array) 
	{} to specify something complex (ojects)
	
	Syntax
		Name : Value
		"" for strings
		no "" for integers
		
		
		
		
